title: Mid Night Club Pt. 1 - The Birth of Japanese Underground Street Racing
description:
In part one of a two-part series, James and Nolan explain the origins of the Mid Night Club, an underground Japanese race team with top-secret members that raced around the streets of Japan from 1982 to 1999, officially speaking.
Follow James on IG and Twitter @jamespumphrey 
Follow Nolan on IG and Twitter @nolanjsykes
Follow Donut @donutmedia, and subscribe to our Youtube and Facebook channels!
